# Example Payloads

## Request Example

```json
{
  "auditRecordId": "recordid1234",
  "publicInfo": {
    "key1": "6676616C756531",
    "key2": "6676616C756532"
  },
  "presentation": <PresentationV1>,
  "verificationRequest": <VerificationRequest>
}
```
